      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, it's basically in pristine, perfect condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' feel! I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all!",
