    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 chassis represents a pinnacle of over-engineered Japanese performance, maintained in a state of mechanical preservation. At its heart is the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration with a flawless transition and factory-spec boost pressure. Power is routed through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox, known for its short-throw precision, and distributed via a factory-equipped Torsen limited-slip differential. The undercarriage reveals a pristine aluminum double-wishbone suspension with all bushings and ball joints exhibiting zero play or dry-rot. The engine bay is clinically clean, with no evidence of heat-cycling fatigue on the vacuum lines or wiring loom. This is a collector-grade example with documented service history, retaining its OEM cooling efficiency and structural integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
