    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this impeccably maintained vehicle that truly defines showroom quality. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and every switch and dial functions with the satisfying, crisp tactile feel of a brand-new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage remains as clean as the engine bay. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than the absolute best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
